{"tid":854690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FCC顛覆當地政府早有前科","createTime":"2018-10-09T14:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T06:07:29.000Z","uid":116471,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"56d5f33673b31ca7078d5113ef5f3dc0f3f0817d","tid":854690,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"在記者會遷到香港的前夕，即1949年4月，國民政府拘捕並判處兩名記者會會員，路透社的格拉咸贊堅斯（Graham Jenkins）及《字林西報》（North China Daily News）的佐治韋尼（George Vine）死刑。<br />\n<br />\n事因剛從南京到上海的贊堅斯報道解放軍橫渡揚子江時，指國軍迅速潰敗；而韋尼供應同一報導給路透社時更連同地圖。贊堅斯首先被捕，同日韋尼亦遭拘禁，兩人拒絕透露新聞來源，被控製造謠言，判處死刑。"},{"pid":"a45944b791782f4f8d7a98abd954e4a3c93a029d","tid":854690,"uid":199590,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:21:05.000Z","msg":"支持香港政府列FCC為非法團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n效法當年 拘捕所有FCC職員並判處死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c363a2032a9b87ecf8642f9a596ed645d65d5866","tid":854690,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"1949年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf6358f2569642feb52ea91041e1f61858044c3","tid":854690,"uid":31907,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a45944b791782f4f8d7a98abd954e4a3c93a029d","tid":854690,"uid":199590,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:21:05.000Z","msg":"支持香港政府列FCC為非法團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n效法當年 拘捕所有FCC職員並判處死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"支持香港人無差別格支解洋人，高鼻曲髮視作洋人論"},{"pid":"aee47332a970f